#: ../../../reference/admonitions.md:1
msgid "Admonitions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/admonitions.md:3
msgid ""
"Admonitions are a great way to include side content, without significantly "
"interrupting the document flow. Sphinx provides several different types of "
"admonitions and allows for the inclusion and nesting of arbitrary content."
msgstr ""

